{"tid":1759094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每晚聽樓下個手足用小號吹榮光已經成為我嘅精神糧食","createTime":"2019-11-27T12:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T13:09:56.000Z","uid":171561,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e23029a8c9e4b3def85becb80a8376c6fb39cd3","tid":1759094,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"已經好多晚係呢個時候聽到<br />\n如果你睇到呢個po 我好想多謝你<br />\n雖然你吹得斷斷續續<br />\n次次都係吹得個前奏 之後就斷下斷下<br />\n但係個種感動我真係唔識形容<br />\n如果我都識樂器就好 可以同你伴奏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我d語氣好似一個愛國撚<br />\n以前會嘲笑d老一輩聽到鄰國國歌會喊<br />\n成日覺得自己係一個Global citizen<br />\n香港只係咁啱係我住嘅地方<br />\n但係而家我想大嗌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我係香港人啊Hi</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4620d6eaedc92714f02ec06e8c2a264f726c95a9","tid":1759094,"uid":38222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都要加緊練習先得<br />\n利申 木結他JJ"},{"pid":"17c4b754e0b2abdd0073eecadcc1100093725d46","tid":1759094,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"識音樂既手足，一齊出黎唱歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"f24b9da576c9ce5d1503e7c574111a31808333f9","tid":1759094,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:05:43.000Z","msg":"屌你我仲練緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1a8ad7819bcaf195efe56998c2944bff292145","tid":1759094,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\